This version brings only small improvements bug fixes: New feature for notes: Change Date of Entry is now available in the ... menu allowing you to adjust dates for your entries easily. Enhanced support for Right to Left RTL languages Improved PDF HTML export functionality: We ve eliminated the extra space above images in PDF exports and now support table formatting in HTML exports. Upgraded Calendar importer: The color of your calendar is now visible in the configuration list and we ve enhanced the handling of multi day events. Please note: this is the last version of Diarly supporting iOS 13. To continue enjoying future updates and features consider upgrading your device s operating system. In case you missed our previous update here s a quick recap: Apple Journaling Suggestions Integration iPhone only : Access personalized topic suggestions by tapping the magic pencil icon above your keyboard during entry editing. Your support means the world to us! If you re enjoying Diarly please consider leaving a rating or review. Thank you!

In this update we ve focused on enhancing your Diarly experience: Weather Import: We ve fixed the glitch where Celsius and Fahrenheit were swapped. Calendar Import: The functionality for importing from calendars should be fully functional. For those who may have missed what we introduced in our last update: New Features: Introducing Widgets! Quotes Widget: Display favorite quotes from selected journal on your screen. Streak Widget: Track and display your journaling streak. Improved Health Integration: Sleep Time: Automatically records your last night s sleep duration. Menstrual Cycle Tracking: Logs period cycles seamlessly. A Big Thank You We extend a heartfelt thank you to each one of you who helped us identify and fix the latest version s issues. Your contributions are invaluable and together we continue to enhance Diarly.

Discover new features to enhance your app experience: Tables: Improve your entries by adding tables with a few simple clicks. Whether you re typing or pasting in your tables they ll help keep you organized and structured. Improved AI Assistant: With our new bio feature you can introduce yourself to the AI Assistant. This allows the Assistant to provide personalized suggestions. Check out our new advice prompt where the AI Assistant dishes out random advice for your day. New Importer Evernote: We ve made it even easier to bring your Evernote content into our app. Seamlessly import your notes from Evernote and continue your journaling journey with us. As always we value your feedback and suggestions. If you encounter any issues or have ideas to share please don t hesitate to reach out to us. Our goal is to make this app your go to choice for journaling. We are constantly working to improve your experience and would love to hear what you think of these updates. If you re enjoying our app please consider taking a few moments to rate and review it on the App Store. Thanks for your support!

Enhanced Audio Transcription: Now transcribe even longer audio files with ease! Improved Accessibility: Our calendar view should work better with voice over enabled. If you encounter any issues please report them to us via email or on our Reddit page. We appreciate your feedback and support. Have a fantastic day!

Introducing the Subscriptions tab under Settings for a hassle free way to view your current subscription status. If you experience any issues with purchases on your device simply use this tab to restore them. Also we ve added an auto save feature for sketches ensuring your work is never lost even if the app unexpectedly closes. A massive thank you to everyone who helped us identify bugs and provided valuable feedback! If you enjoy using our app please consider leaving us a rating or review. Your support is greatly appreciated!

If you missed our last update here s a recap of the new features we recently added to Diarly: We ve introduced AI powered daily prompts that generate random affirmations to help you start each day on a positive note. We ve also made it easier for you to transition from Stoic.App to Diarly with our new import feature. In addition this version includes bug fixes for several issues that were reported by our users after the last update. We worked hard to address these problems and decided to release this update ahead of schedule to ensure a smoother experience for everyone. Thank you for your continued support of Diarly. If you have any feedback or questions please don t hesitate to reach out.

We ve got some exciting updates for the Diarly app! First off we ve added AI powered daily prompts that generate personalized affirmations to help you start your day on a positive note. We ve also added a new feature that allows you to easily transition from the Stoic App to Diarly with our Stoic App importer. Lastly we ve made significant under the hood improvements to enhance your overall experience using Diarly. Your feedback is essential to us! If you have any suggestions or run into any issues please don t hesitate to reach out. Let s work together to keep refining and improving Diarly for our fantastic community of users. Enjoy the new update and please consider leaving a rating in the App Store. Thanks for your support!

You can now easily transcribe your audio notes. Simply click on the three dots menu for your audio note and select Add Transcription to your Note . This feature is perfect for those who prefer reading over listening and makes it easy to organize your notes. We are excited to announce that Diarly now includes an AI assistant powered by the OpenAI GPT 3 language model. You can now ask questions directly from your favorite journaling app and get answers from our AI assistant. Please note: Diarly does not share your data with OpenAI except the questions you ask the assistant. The answers provided by our AI assistant may not always be accurate or correct. This is a premium feature and as part of your Diarly subscription will get free credits every week. 2.5.8: Fix for new bug copy paste would not work correctly. We hope you enjoy using our new AI assistant and we would appreciate it if you could leave us a 5 star rating if you like the app.
